sequenceDiagram
  participant W as Writer
  participant L as Sharded WAL<br/>on-disk file
  participant F as Stream file<br/>(page cache)
  participant R as Live readers

  par append
    W->>L: stage record
  and
    W->>F: write once into page cache
  end
  F-->>R: publish tail, wake readers
  L-->>W: 2xx (only after durable)
